!! 0.1.0

* First working version of Zest plugin.
* Supports creation, editing, and deletion of domains, categories, and theses.
* Categories can be linked to multiple domains.
* Each category requires at least one thesis.
* Deleting a category removes all its theses.
* Prevents orphaned categories and theses.
* Includes demo data and documentation.
* Integrates with SRS plugin for interval repetition.
* Initial UI for managing domains, categories, and theses.